lead_paragraph: The chairman of the House Financial Services Committee issued a subpoena to the Federal Reserve to provide documents related to a leak of information to a newsletter.

headline.print_headline: Lawmaker Subpoenas Fed, Seeking Evidence of a Leak
headline.main: Lawmaker Subpoenas Fed, Seeking Evidence of a Leak

snippet: The chairman of the House Financial Services Committee issued a subpoena to the Federal Reserve to provide documents related to a leak of information to a newsletter.
abstract: Rep Jeb Hensarling, Texas Republican, announces issuance of subpoena to Federal Reserve for documents concerning 2012 leak of confidential interest-rate information to financial newsletter.
